{"tid":2000879,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"內地設廠港商獲豁免強制檢疫 每間企業今起可申2名額","createTime":"2020-05-04T07:00:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-04T10:46:43.000Z","uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"aa526e42bf07bf6a3f01fffaafbe9e85fcd2daf0","tid":2000879,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T07:00:49.000Z","msg":"新冠肺炎疫情緩和，一些對香港經濟發展有利益的跨境生產作業需求日增，政府今(4日)公布，在內地從事生產作業的港商可豁免接受強制檢疫，其中持有商業登記及在內地設生產線的港商，即日起可申請最多兩名人員，例如公司負責人或指定員工，返港後豁免接受14日強制檢疫。工業貿易署今起會處理有關申請。<br />\n<br />\n政府稱，獲豁免人士到內地只可前往，及逗留於其企業內地廠房所在的城市，以支援該廠房運作和業務。期間亦須採取一切所需的防護措施以保障個人衞生，及避免不必要的社交接觸。有關人士回港後，仍須於留港期間接受由衞生署安排的醫學監測，以及佩戴口罩和每天量度體溫，並向衞生署呈報任何不適。<br />\n<br />\n另外，工業貿易署在處理申請時，會按需要諮詢香港工業總會、香港中華廠商聯合會，以及相關政策局和部門，向獲豁免人士發出的授權書，並列明豁免條件。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200504/bkn-20200504135019309-0504_00822_001.html?eventsection=hk_news&amp;eventid=402883476ed4097c016f5a39f2c63fde\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200504%2Fbkn-20200504135019309-0504_00822_001.html%3Feventsection%3Dhk_news%26eventid%3D402883476ed4097c016f5a39f2c63fde&d=LQBsT8b49a%2FdXTDbQfnWX2dKmUD4oZ9Yq66eb74BBG8%3D&h=97f296ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200504/bkn-20200504135019309-0504_00822_001.html?eventsection=hk_news&amp;eventid=402883476ed4097c016f5a39f2c63fde</a>"},{"pid":"ee24ff382b811d5ee82f050d9e340df30d8825ab","tid":2000879,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T07:01:53.000Z","msg":"肯定一大堆一人公司"},{"pid":"753c69cdf1b73a29c74a55fbf13692eb5175db1c","tid":2000879,"uid":77196,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T07:04:23.000Z","msg":"第N波疫情準備 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea3a2f90d6cf79cbb5033c38cca66c1763bf8ffa","tid":2000879,"uid":112416,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T07:05:53.000Z","msg":"每間公司可以申請兩名員工成為免疫人士"},{"pid":"5e58324a68a15e1227e5267fbd9fa987fe27c035","tid":2000879,"uid":278219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T07:07:05.000Z","msg":"呢個好似之前已經可以申請"},{"pid":"776c5c14204b8469718cdb609a2de18c0f3a2c2d","tid":2000879,"uid":87809,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T08:06:48.000Z","msg":"但唔係番上大陸又要檢疫14日咩？有咩意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db037ff33c0cc841a0d92c08afe902ea2f2cebe9","tid":2000879,"uid":82938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"776c5c14204b8469718cdb609a2de18c0f3a2c2d","tid":2000879,"uid":87809,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T08:06:48.000Z","msg":"但唔係番上大陸又要檢疫14日咩？有咩意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T10:46:43.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}